			<h1 class="text-white text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold flex flex-row gap-x-2 pb-5 lg:pb-10">Hey, I'm Gabriel <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/gabriel-rossy-baptista-y-vedia/" class="flex justify-center items-center"><Badge>Available for hire</Badge></a></h1>
			<h2 class="text-lg lg:text-2xl text-wrap max-w-[700px]"><span class="text-yellow-200/90">Junior Web Developer</span> from <span class="text-blue-200">Montevideo, UruguayðŸ‡ºðŸ‡¾</span>. I like to do mobile apps with <span class="text-blue-500/90">Flutter</span>.</h2>
			
			<ul class="flex gap-4 my-4 flex-wrap">
				<li>
					<SocialPill href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/gabriel-rossy-baptista-y-vedia/">
						<LinkedinIcon class="size-5 md:size-6"/>
						LinkedIn
					</SocialPill>
				</li>
				<li>
					<SocialPill href="https://github.com/gaboxdeveloper">
						<GithubIcon class="size-5 md:size-6"/>
						GitHub
					</SocialPill>
				</li>
				<li>
					<SocialPill> 
						<MailIcon class="size-5 md:size-6"/>
						grossy.sjb@gmail.com
					</SocialPill>
